programme.title: Drama On 2 – Dia Anak Jeneral Ep5
programme.desc: Kalau sudah berbintikan Hambali, semuanya akan diatur termasuklah calon suami. Bila Leftenan Jeneral kata hitam, maka hitamlah warnanya. Syirin harus akur. Kehadiran Zakhif telah mengoyahkan hati Syirin. Saling terpesona, hati dibaluti bahagia. Tapi Zakhif sedar siapa dia. Bagaimana kuat cinta mereka, hebat lagi risiko bakal menanti. Lalu Zakhif cuba menjauh. Namun, Syirin semakin mendekat dekat satu tekad. Zakhif mula pening. Mampukah dia hantar rombongan meminang? Yang nak dipinang adalah anak kepada Leftenan Jeneral Hambali. Kisah cinta yang mudah menjadi payah kerana dia anak Jeneral!

programme.title: Drama On 2 – Peluang
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kebimbangan Pak usop 70 tahun terhadap masa depan cucunya yang menghidapi autisme. Kamil berusia 12 tahun dijaga datuknya Pak Usop setelah kematian ibu bapanya yang terlibat dengan nahas jalanraya ketika dia berumur 10 tahun. Kamil dikesan menghidapi penyakit ini pada usianya 6 tahun yang menyebabkan beliau suka menyendiri dan tidak suka berkomunikasi dengan orang sekeliling.

programme.title: Variety On 2 – NICTSeD 2024 (Live)

Wacana ICT ini membincangkan isu-isu keselamatan siber semasa bertujuan untuk memupuk kesedaran mengenai penggunaan teknologi dan Internet secara positif, beretika dan bertanggungjawab dalam kalangan murid-murid sekolah di seluruh Negara.

programme.title: Hiburan On 2 – #Influencer Ep2

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep16
programme.desc: Shariff terus meminati Hani dia memujuk Yusri untuk menceritakan sejauh mana hal Hani. Dalam masa yang sama Shariff ada masalah keluarga berpunca bapanya. Dia juga akui kepada Dzul dan pernah menghubungi Hani untuk temujanji, tetapi Hani tegas menolak. Nizam yang baru bekerja di Johor Bahru menerima kunjungan mengejut Sheila. Di peringkat mula Nizam bukan sahaja memarahi Sheila tetapi tidak mahu menerima kedatangan dan melayannya. Dia juga mengherdik dengan kata-kata kesat. Sehingga Sheila merayu agar memberi ruang dan peluang akhirnya terbuka juga hati Nizam. Lantaran itu, Sheila berkesempatan memberi tahu secara serius kepada Nizam bahawa Mizan amat sayangkan Hani dan lupakan sahaja hasratnya. Setakat ini Nizam masih tidak percaya. Apa pun dia juga menyatakan kepada Sheila dia akan mencari rumah mereka di Johor Bahru dan meminta Sheila pulang. Mizan delima kerana membayangkan keadaan yang amat tidak sesuai berlaku jika Sharif rakan baiknya menghawini Hani dan mereka pula sepejabat. Dalam pada itu Suraya pula cuba mengapi-apikan rumah tangganya. Antara Mizan dengan Hani masih dingin, tetapi Hani lebih tenang dan masing-masing tidak abaikan tanggungjawab rumah tangga.

programme.title: Pembancuh Kopi Mr Vampire S1 Ep28
programme.desc: Nuzul mengambil peluang ini untuk merapatkan hubungannya dengan Irsyad. Pada suatu malam, Nuzul dan Irsyad bermain catur. Oleh kerana Nuzul menang, Irsyad dikehendaki untuk mengisi borang yang telah disediakan Nuzul. Di dalam borang tersebut tercatat soalan tentang nama bekas teman wanita Irsyad dan nama restoran kegemaran Irsyad. Nuzul mempunyai rancangan untuk memikat hati suaminya. Dia berkunjung ke setiap restoran mewah yang menjadi kegemaran Irsyad dan cuba mendapatkan resipi setiap makanan kegemaran suaminya melalui chef-chef di restoran berkenaan. Nuzul nekad melakukan apa saja demi mengelakkan Irsyad memadukannya dengan perempuan lain. Setelah berjaya mengumpul semua resipi, Nuzul pulang ke rumah. Namun dia terkejut dengan tengkingan Irsyad dan suaminya itu juga telah melempar fitnah bahawa Nuzul berlaku curang. Nuzul terkejut.

programme.title: Suamiku Mr Blind S1 Ep30
programme.desc: Ain sukar untuk bersalin dan berkali-kali mohon maaf kepada Aidil. Aidil juga minta maaf atas segala perbuatannya pada Ain selama ini. Akhirnya Ain selamat melahirkan anak lelaki yang diberi nama Adib Mukhris. Melihat Adib kali pertama sudah membuahkan rasa sayang pada Ain. Dia terfikir-fikir janjinya dengan Aidil sepanjang tempoh berpantang. Dia tidak mahu berpisah dengan Adib. Aidil berkeras mengingatkan Ain untuk menurut janji-janji di dalam surat itu. Ain tidak sangka Aidil sekejam itu. Ain rasa menyesal dengan janji yang dibuatnya dan mohon agar Aidil melupakan segalanya. Aidil sengaja provoke Ain untuk ingat apa permintaannya. Sampailah Ain merayu yang dia tidak sanggup hendak berpisah dengan Adib dan Aidil. Ain ajak rujuk dan itu yang membuatkan Aidil menyuruh Ain membawa kembali perjanjian itu. Rupa-rupanya surat perjanjian itu ialah wasiat Aidil untuk Ain dan anak mereka. Ain gembira Aidil tidak mengikut apa yang diingini dan Aidil gembira Ain sudah sedar dan kembali sayang kepadanya.

programme.desc: Sam amat takutkan Julia, kerana Julia menyimpan banyak rahsianya. Sam mendedahkan rahsia sebenar kepada Julia bahawa anak dalam kandungan Wani itu merupakan anak kepada bos Sam. Namun, salah faham berlaku apabila Badrul ternampak Mona dengan koleksi gambar lamanya bersama Fareez. Berlaku pertelingkahan, sehingga Mona mengakui masih terfikirkan lelaki itu. Badrul semakin putus asa dengan hubungan mereka. Irfan dan Mimi cuba membantu merapatkan mereka. Menerusi perbincangan dengan Julia, Irfan dan Mimi mengesyaki keikhlasan Abang Lok. programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep17
programme.desc: Hani masih bersedih kerana Mizan seperti tidak menerimanya. Sedang Hani duduk di sebuah kedai minum, kebetulan Suraya nampaknya, tanpa diundang dia mengapi-apikan Hani. Pilihan terbaik hanya bercerai Mizan demi keselamatan dan kebahagiaan ibu bapanya dan Nizam akan buat apa saja. Hani beredar dan ke kedai lain, kebetulan Shariff datang ke kedai itu menegurnya yang masih bersedih. Hani berbual dengan Shariff atas dasar rakan dan "client", perniagaan Hani secara on line. Hani menerima pelawaan Shariff untuk menghantarnya pulang. Nizam mengetahui lalu marah dan amat cemburu dan sekali lagi mengulangi serta bertegas akan mengahwininya juga. Semuanya menambah kekusutan Hani. Selepas bersembahyang Hani berdoa seperti kebiasaannya. Sebelah malamnya, Mizan kelihatan positif membuatkan Hani lega. Sementara itu, ibu dan bapa mereka bersama Sheila dalam perjalanan ke rumah mereka. Kedatangan mereka kerana ingin melawat ibu dan bapa Sheila kemalangan. Sebelum itu Nizam tiba dahulu di rumah mereka bagi tujuan yang sama. Semasa Mizan menyiapkan bilik ibu dan bapanya termasuk membawa barang Hani ke biliknya (Hani dan Mizan masih tidur di bilik berasingan), Nizam berkesempatan memujuk rayu Hani lagi, malahan rancangannya, Sheila akan diceraikan. Hani sentiasa mengalih perbualan Nizam sehingga mengatakan dia telah mengandung. Hani dan Mizan juga bertingkah laku begitu mesra kepada Nizam sekali gus terhadap ibu bapa mereka.

programme.title: Dia Menantu Rahsia Ep12
programme.desc: Memaparkan Melissa masih di rumah keluarga Syakir dan bertindak seperti orang gaji. Walaupun begitu mereka makan bersama, amalan ketika ada Mak Tun lagi. Selesai makan, Melissa akan balik kali ini puan Sarah merestui Syakir menghantarnya, kerana lewat. Sebelum itu, di dapur Nora ternampak Melissa dan Syakir. Semasa berlepas balik, Syakir dipesan ibunya agar jangan kemana-mana lagi. Malah puan Sarah merungut kelaluan Syakir terhadap Melissa. Lalu tuan Suhaimi menegurnya itu nak jadikan Melissa sebagai sasaran baru pula. Nora yang berbual dengan Shamsul sebelum tidur juga nampak Syakir seperti ada hubungan tertentu. Shamsul nampak pun begitu juga mungkin adiknya bercinta Melissa. Bagi Nora, tahu-tahu mereka telah pun berkahwin tetapi dirahsiakan. Shamsul mencelah jika hingga peringkat itu tidak mungkin, kerana dia tahu akan adiknya itu. Sebelum itu Syakir berbual dengan keluarganya yang dia mengesahkan akan ke Kazakastan selama 3 bulan bermula bulan hadapan. Sekali gus Melissa terdengar, agak sebak juga dia di dapur tetapi dapat mengawal situasi itu. Masa telah berlalu sebulan, sementara hubungan Shamsul dan Nora kini baik, Nora melupakan apa yang berlalu, malah hubungan Nora dengan ibunya juga baik. Melissa pula tahu dirinya dan dia terus merendah diri. Syakir sekadar seperti biasa berkongsi pengalamannya terkini dengan Jenny. Terkini puan Sarah datang bersama Nora mengajak Melissa untuk keluar bersama kononnya dia ingin membuat satu majlis. Syakir tidak tahu menahu, cuma hal ini diketahuinya setelah mendapati Melissa sedang bersama ibunya. Syakir mengadu kepada Shamsul ketika mereka sama-sama di pejabat. Alasan Syakir tindakan ibunya dia tidak menyukai kerana Melissa bekerja dengannya. Engku Razi, Engku Kamelia dan ibunya bersama, sekali lagi Engku Razi mengingatkan ibunya bahawa Syakir tidak mahukan Kamelia dan meminta adiknya jangan terhegeh-hegeh dan kini dia juga merasa malu. Kamelia sekali lagi menyalahkan ibunya dan Kamelia langsung tidak peduli, dia mahukan Syakir sebagai miliknya. Dia bertekad, dia telah mula sukakan Syakir sejak sama-sama kecil lagi. Apabila Melissa balik berseorangan sebagai arahan puan Sarah, Syakir mempersoalkan Melissa tidak maklumkannya. Kini hubungan mereka tidak semesra seperti dahulu, Melissa mengakui dirinya sebagai pembantu rumah. Syakir pula menghadapi masalah, apabila Melissa maklumkan ibunya ingin adakah majlis kenduri di rumah mereka sebelum dia ke Kazakastan. Dalam masa itu puan Sarah bertandang ke rumah Engku Maimunah selain memberitahu dia akan adakan majlis kenduri, dia juga memberitahu Syakir telah membeli rumah, seolah-olah dia begitu bersedia untuk berkahwin. Dalam pada Engku Maimunah dan puan Sarah agak gembira, Syakir mengetuk bilik Melissa. Syakir akui kali ini dia akan berterus terang dan akan menghadapi apa yang mereka berdua akan tempuhi. Di hari majlis ringkas keluarga, keluarga Engku Maimunah juga di jemput. Zamer pemandu enggan masuk, tetapi ternampak Melissa dan merungut berseorangan apa yang dia di situ. Engku Razi pula yang nampak Melissa di muka pintu dengan sinis menyatakan kepada Syakir yang pembantu rumahnya cantik. puan Sarah selepas berdoa, membuat kejutan mengumumkan yang Syakir akan ditunangkan dengan Kamelia. Sedangkan Syakir di lihat dan tidak dilayan oleh Syakir, Syakir dan Melissa memandang antara satu dengan lain. Dalam celah itu, Engku Razi cuba mendapat perhatian kepada Melissa.

programme.desc: Rasya Aleeya dan Syed Reeza jatuh cinta melalui SMS tanpa mengetahui latar belakang masing-masing. Rasya yang paranoid dan takut ditinggalkan ragu dengan Reeza, yang dikenal sebagai 'kaki flirt'. Setelah Rasya menikahi Fahmi karena pengaruh temannya, Adri, Reeza patah hati dan keluarganya merencanakan pernikahannya dengan Hilda. Ketika Reeza bertemu kembali dengan Rasya di Dubai dan mengetahui dia telah menjadi janda, mereka menyadari perasaan mereka belum padam. Meskipun awalnya ragu, Rasya dan Reeza akhirnya menikah, mengatasi keraguan dan kesalahpahaman mereka.

programme.desc: Hani masih bersedih kerana Mizan seperti tidak menerimanya. Sedang Hani duduk di sebuah kedai minum, kebetulan Suraya nampaknya, tanpa diundang dia mengapi-apikan Hani. Pilihan terbaik hanya bercerai Mizan demi keselamatan dan kebahagiaan ibu bapanya dan Nizam akan buat apa saja. Hani beredar dan ke kedai lain, kebetulan Shariff datang ke kedai itu menegurnya yang masih bersedih. Hani berbual dengan Shariff atas dasar rakan dan "client", perniagaan Hani secara on line. Hani menerima pelawaan Shariff untuk menghantarnya pulang. Nizam mengetahui lalu marah dan amat cemburu dan sekali lagi mengulangi serta bertegas akan mengahwininya juga. Semuanya menambah kekusutan Hani. Selepas bersembahyang Hani berdoa seperti kebiasaannya. Sebelah malamnya, Mizan kelihatan positif membuatkan Hani lega. Sementara itu, ibu dan bapa mereka bersama Sheila dalam perjalanan ke rumah mereka. Kedatangan mereka kerana ingin melawat ibu dan bapa Sheila kemalangan. Sebelum itu Nizam tiba dahulu di rumah mereka bagi tujuan yang sama. Semasa Mizan menyiapkan bilik ibu dan bapanya termasuk membawa barang Hani ke biliknya (Hani dan Mizan masih tidur di bilik berasingan), Nizam berkesempatan memujuk rayu Hani lagi, malahan rancangannya, Sheila akan diceraikan. Hani sentiasa mengalih perbualan Nizam sehingga mengatakan dia telah mengandung. Hani dan Mizan juga bertingkah laku begitu mesra kepada Nizam sekali gus terhadap ibu bapa mereka.

programme.title: Jodoh Sebelah Pintu S1 Ep29
programme.desc: Mimi dapati Abang Lok langsung tidak sama dengan Fareez , dan merasakan Mona mungkin sudah dipukau bomoh itu. Irfan pula mendapatkan bantuan Ezrin untuk mencari perkaitan di antara Abang Lok dan Dr. Norma. Badrul hilang punca dan terus cuba menyerang Abang Lok. Abang Lok akhirnya mendedahkan perbuatan Dr. Norma yang sebenar. Dr. Norma terpaksa menjelaskan punca perbuatannya. Dia sudah lama menyimpan perasaan terhadap Badrul. Dia juga mencemburui prestasi Badrul di hospital itu. Satu-satunya cara untuk mengatasi semua ini ialah dengan memastikan Badrul menjadi miliknya. Irfan melaporkan perbuatan ini kepada pihak hospital. Dr. Norma terus melarikan diri. Amirul dan Taufik bergaduh besar kerana Julia. Julia merasakan dirinya benar-benar dicintai. Julia akhirnya memilih Taufik.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep18
programme.desc: Semua keluarga Hani ada di rumahnya. Nizam mahu tidak mahu terpaksa menerima Sheila dan anaknya tidur sebilik. Sementara itu hubungan Hani dan Mizan yang mesra seperti bukan berlakon lagi. Dalam pada itu Nizam tetap menyukai Hani dan Hani tahu mengelak dan berbalas cakapnya. Mereka sekeluarga juga ke hospital. Di hospital, hubungan Nizam dan Sheila masih tegang. Nizam berterus terang dia hanya berlakon jika berjumpa dengan ibu Sheila kerana dia akan berkahwin dengan Hani dan Sheila tetap akan diceraikan. Demi untuk nampak tenang, Sheila mengalah, sanggup terima apa yang dihajat Nizam. Walau pun begitu dia meminta masa. Sheila melawat ibunya di wad, walau pun dia berkata-kata telah berkahwin dan memohon maaf tetapi ibunya tidak sedar ketika itu. Sheila juga bersemuka sekali lagi dengan Hani dan terang-terang Hani menafikan segala hasrat Nizam dan didengari Nizam. Sementara itu Shariff tetap menyukai Hani dan meminta bantuan ibu saudaranya Umairah isteri Datuk Fuad menjadi wakilnya agar Hani kelak menjadi isterinya. Dalam masa yang sama Datuk Fuad, suami Umairah curang telah mengamalkan rasuah membolehkan Ah Meng mudah perolehi tender sepatutnya diperolehi syarikat mereka. Semuanya gara-gara Suraya. Berikutan itu Shariff diminta Umairah utamakan menyelamatkan syarikat mereka. Umairah juga memaklumkan Shariff berdasarkan biodata Hani, Hani itu adalah adik kandungnya.

programme.desc: Hujung bulan? Poket kering? Bajet kecik tetapi selera besar? Jangan risau, dengan modal RM20.00, anda boleh menyediakan 2 jenis masakan western dengan cepat dan mudah. Dapur Bujang Western menampilkan Fendi Balas Raja Lawak sebagai host merangkap chef untuk memastikan perut anda terus kenyang tanpa risaukan wang ringgit.

programme.title: Dia Menantu Rahsia Ep13
programme.desc: Memaparkan Melissa kini tahu perancangan puan Sarah yang telah umum pertunangan antara Syakir dengan Engku Melissa. Melissa juga tahu dan tidak berang, malah meminta Syakir jangan berdekatan dan berbual dengannya terutama ketika puan Sarah belum berlepas. Sebelum puan Sarah pulang, dia meminta Melissa lakukan segala pembersihan perlu terutama mengemas dapur, Melissa akur. Di rumah, Nora perasan yang Syakir memandang Melissa dan Melissa agak terkejut tetapi tenang apabila puan Sarah umumkan. Suaminya tidak perasan tetapi jika benar berlaku tentunya Syakir memberitahunya. Tuan Suhaimi menegur isterinya yang kelihatan riang, selamba menjawab puan Sarah kerana satu kerja telah selesai. Cuma tuan Suhaimi akui tidak semestinya Syakir setuju kerana dia tidak dimaklumkan. Tuan Suhaimi juga menyatakan Syakir tidak membantah kerana menjaga air muka orang tua. Dalam pada itu Syakir menegur Melissa yang bertungkus lumus dan dia meminta Melissa berhenti dan rehat sert tidur. Melissa pula terus tetap dengan panggilan tuan Syak kepada Syakir, ditegur Syakir tetapi Melissa telah menyatakan dia telah biasa. Syakir akan menjelaskan segala-galanya pada keesokannya. Esoknya Syakir telah sedia sarapan pagi, Melissa letih dan tertidur, malah Syakir lakukan segala kerja bersih hingga selesai. Dalam pada itu Syakir hanya berjumpa Jenny seperti kelaziman, meluahkan segala apa yang dia bermasalah sekarang. Apa pun terjadi, Syakir akui akan terus mempertahanan Melissa walaupun agak sukar untuk menentang atau berterus terang bimbangkan kesihatan ibunya. Dalam pada itu sepupu Melissa yang balik ke kampung memaklumkan hubungan antara Melissa dan Syakir begitu baik. Lalu ibu Melissa rasa lega dan meminta jikanya berjumpa Melissa, mintakan Syakir membawa kedua ibu dan bapanya, paling kurang untuk berbincang bagi majlis ringkas sebagai mewar-warkan mereka telah berkahwin. Di hari lain sepupu Melissa sampaikan hasrat ibu Melissa, Melissa terdiam sekejap tetapi seolah-olah tenang dan akui dia akan berbincang dengan Syakir. Kini Kamelia kelihatan agak gembira, tetapi Zamer yang sentiasa menemaninya berharap waspada kerana Melissa yang kelihatan pernah bersama Syakir, kini ada di rumah Syakir. Dalam pertemuan antara Syakir dan Kamelia sekali lagi Syakir anggapkan mereka sebagai rakan sahaja. Kamelia secara biasa, mengesyorkan apa salahnya jika mereka bersama, lagi pun ibunya sangat mengharapkan. Puan Sarah datang lagi dengan mengejut ke rumah anak menantunya. Dia menegur Melissa membawa sepupu ke dalam rumah, dia juga menegur Melissa basuhkan bajunya sendiri bersekali dengan baju Syakir. Dalam pada itu Engku Razi yang berbincang hal Syakir dan Kamelia, Engku Razi sekali lagi meminta ibunya mengingati reaksi dan muka Syakir apabila ibunya umumkan. Ibunya hanya andaikan pandangan itu sebagai pandangan peribadi Engku Razi, sebaliknya ibunya tahu yang Engku Razi pula meminati orang gaji Syakir(Melissa). Engku Razi pula menafikannya. Lantaran itu ibunya memuji Razi kerana kelak maruah keluarganya akan jatuh. Syakir sekali lagi bergeseran dengan ibunya dan sekali menegaskan dia tidak mahu kahwin dengan Kamelia. Syakir balik ke rumahnya, dia kesudahan dengan ibunya. Ketika bersama Kamelia Syakir sekali lagi memaklumkan hasrat ibunya, ibunya juga ada sakit jantung, jadi Syakir berjanji masih tidak sesuai untuk berterus terang. Sekali lagi meyakinkan Melissa yang antara mereka berdua akan sehidup semati. Melissa juga sedih akan hal tugas Syakir akan ke Kazakastan, tetapi redza. Di hari lain puan Sarah meminta pemandunya menjemput Melissa dan kemudiannya dia di arah untuk membeli belah untuk persiapan "hi-tea", Zaker cuba menganggunya, mujur Razi datang, Razi mengambil kesempatan hantar Melissa dan luahkan perasaannya kepada Melissa.

programme.title: Anggun Mikayla Ep07
programme.desc: Perjalanan hidup Mikayla sentiasa bersimpang-siur dengan dugaan sejak dia mencelikkan mata birunya ke dunia. Status kelahirannya membuatkan dia seringkali menerima cacian penduduk kampung dan menjadi mangsa buli semasa kecil. Mekap adalah cara Mikayla menidakkan kewujudannya sendiri. Dia berselindung di sebalik rambut palsu hitam untuk menyorokkan rambut auburnnya serta mengenakan pelbagai jenis mekap untuk menggelapkan warna kulit kerana keinginannya untuk tampak Melayu. Siang, Mikayla bekerja sebagai jurumekap artis dan apabila malam tiba, dia menjelma sebagai pontianak. Pertemuan Mikayla dengan Idriz dalam satu insiden lucu telah mencipta satu hubungan aneh yang tidak bernama. Dalam diam, Idriz menyimpan rasa tetapi keinginannya terbatas kerana tanggungjawabnya pada keluarga. Jurugambar yang bekerja bersamanya, Asif yang suka mengusik Mikayla mulai tersedar yang usikannya sudah bertukar menjadi perasaan sebenar. Tetapi, dia terlajak memikat pelakon popular bernama Andria, sebelum tersedar tentang perasaannya terhadap Mikayla. Sedang Mikayla dalam keadaan celaru, lelaki dari masa silamnya, Aidan pula muncul kembali, menagih kemaafan kerana meninggalkan parut panjang di dahinya. Aidan yang kini sudah bergelar pelakon popular cuba memadamkan kenangan sakit mereka demi merebut hati yang dirinduinya itu. Tetapi, impian Mikayla hanya satu, berhadapan dengan masa silamnya dan mencantas kebencian mama. Cinta bukan destinasi yang diimpi. Namun, hatinya terus menjadi buruan oleh tiga orang lelaki.

programme.desc: Filem ini mengisahkan liku-liku kehidupan yang dilalui oleh bekas ahli kumpulan muzik rock terkenal di era 90an, Rimba Bara. Namun kerana gejala dadah, masalah peribadi yang tidak terkawal dan kemalangan ngeri yang menimpa, kehidupan anggota kumpulan musnah. Seorang yang koma kembali sedar, membawa sinar baru apabila dia berjaya menguruskan kumpulan muzik rock baru menggunakan nama kumpulan lama; Rimba Bara II diterajui oleh pemuda yang juga jirannya. Pelbagai cabaran dan halangan ditempuhi sebelum kumpulan mereka berjaya dan menempa nama dalam industri muzik rock tanah air. Di akhir penceritaan dibekal dengan semangat kental dan sentiasa positif dalam hidup, pengurus dan semua ahli kumpulan pemuzik rock berjaya dan mencapai cita masing-masing sekali gus kehidupan yang bahagia.

programme.title: Rien Pembunuh Berantai
programme.desc: Rein, seorang lelaki muda dengan masa lalu yang kelam, adalah pelaku kepada mangsa yang dicacatkan yang ditemui di dalam beg pakaian. Dia dibuli oleh kawan-kawannya, ibunya mempunyai hubungan sulit dengan lelaki lain, dan gadis yang dia cintai mengkhianati lelaki lain. Suatu hari, Rein dikehendaki polis dan kini menjadi buruan polis.

programme.desc: Imran membunuh Ajeeb dan Uzair bersumpah untuk membalas dendam. Tanpa berfikir panjang Hatta mahu segera menyerang Imran tetapi Uzair mahu memastikan rakan-rakannya selamat. programme.title: Santau Merasuk Ep 12 Ep12
programme.desc: MAT muncul di saat akhir, dan berjaya menyelamatkan Nina daripada serangan ECHA. ECHA pengsan selepas kuasa hitam di dalam tubuhnya itu telah diluluhkan MAT. MAT memberitahu pada NINA apa yang dipesan DAWAMI padanya berkaitan HALIM. HALIM dalam bahaya bila diganggui makhluk yang terus memburunya dari alam khayalannya hinggalah ke dunia nyata. DAWAMI menyelamatkan situasi HALIM dan sekaligus menghapuskan ilmu ain yang terkena padanya. DAWAMI bawa HALIM pulang ke rumah.

programme.title: Sacred Riana 2: Bloody Mary
programme.desc: Riana ke asrama sekolah Elodia dengan harapan dapat mencari anak patung Riani yang hilang. Para pelajar di situ sering melakukan ritual dengan cermin, iaitu Bloody Mary. Ia yang pada asalnya hanya untuk menakutkan pelajar baru, bertukar menjadi bencana apabila roh cuba mencederakan pelajar. Anak patung Riani didakwa sebagai dalang di sebalik bencana ini. Riana terperangkap dalam dilema antara membawa balik anak patungnya, atau mencari jawapan kepada pelbagai ketakutan yang berlaku.

programme.title: Big Match
programme.desc: Choi Ik-Ho ialah bintang seni mempertahankan diri yang mempunyai bakat dalam aksi dan jenaka. Tetapi suatu hari, dia dijebak kerana membunuh. Ace ialah perancang permainan, yang membuat permainan untuk kelas atasan Korea. Dia adalah penjahat yang menjadikan bandar menjadi papan permainan besar melalui teknologi. Ace dan Choi Ik-Ho menjadi musuh apabila Choi Ik-Ho melompat ke dalam permainan untuk menyelamatkan adiknya.

programme.title: Kapsul
programme.desc: Kapsul masa wawasan 2020 yang ditanam oleh Tun Dr. Mahathir Mohamad telah dicuri dan membawa Zohri kembali ke masa lalu. Zohri kini terperangkap di tengah-tengah pergolakan bangsa Melayu untuk mencapai kemerdekaan dan membawa bangsa Melayu keluar dari belenggu kemiskinan. Zohri melihat dan merasai sendiri erti perjuangan umatnya yang tidak pernah dibayangkannya selama ini. Dia lihat, dia rasa dan kini dia mula faham betapa peritnya liku-liku sejarah negara dan bangsa. Perjalanan Zohri berterusan dari satu zaman ke satu zaman dan tiada siapa yang dapat mengembalikannya ke zamannya melainkan dirinya sendiri.

programme.title: Born To Fight
programme.desc: Daew ialah seorang polis yang telah menangkap penyerang jahat Jeneral Yang, tetapi pasangannya terbunuh dalam kes itu dan Daew menjadi tertekan. Bagaimanapun, kakaknya meminta dia menyertainya dan beberapa rakan atletnya ke sebuah kampung kecil untuk memberi makanan dan mainan kepada penduduk kampung. Apa yang bermula sebagai perjalanan untuk membantu orang ramai bertukar menjadi mimpi ngeri apabila anak buah Yang tiba di kampung dan mengambil alih, menuntut pembebasan Yang atau peluru berpandu nuklear akan melanda Bangkok. Apabila penduduk kampung dibunuh kiri dan kanan, Daew dan para atlet mesti memulakan revolusi menentang kezaliman sebelum terlambat.

programme.desc: Nia mengakui kepada Ibrahim yang ada saka ingin mendampinginya, tetapi dia menolak. Sementara itu dia juga menceritakan bahawa Puteri Jarum Permata adalah menjadi amalan keluarganya sebagai pelindung, tetapi akhirnya ini saka Gelam suka mengganguinya bila dia hendak datang. Dalam pada itu dengan tiba-tiba, Pak Abas dirasuk oleh saka Gelam, tetapi dapat dipulihkan oleh Ibrahim. Manakala Ibrahim setelah bekerjasama dengan kumpulan aktivis paranormal telah dapat berkomunikasi dengan lembaga putih. Kesempatan itu dia telah memberi amaran agar jangan ganggu sesiapa. Manakala saka Gelam telah berkomunikasi dengan lembaga putih lalu memberi amaran dan marahmarah. Dalam pada itu Ibrahim yang terpikat dengan Zeti telah membuat satu janji temu. Di pertemuan itu, Zeti yang bermata duitan juga berkecimpung belajar memuja-memuja orang agar terpengaruh. Dia tahu Datin Salina banyak wang dan bermasalah kerana anak lelakinya tidak setuju dijodohkan dengan Nia. Dengan itu Zeti telah mengajak Ibrahim mencari jalan agar Nia sukakan anak Datin Salina. Dalam situasi ini Ibrahim menolak membuatkan Zeti merajuk dan beredar.

programme.title: Jangan Ikut Aku Ep 12 Ep12
programme.desc: Dalam episod akhir ini, Akil bermimpi mengahwini Cikgu Shila dan mendapat seorang cahaya mata dan mereka berdua selalu mendampingi empat saka itu. Sebenarnya, Chikgu Shila telah menjauhi diri daripada Akil kerana kegagalannya memberitahu tentang empat saka yang mendampinginya. Akil berazam menghalau saka-saka tersebut dan minta pertolongan bomoh Anjang Itam. Anjang Itam bersetuju dengan syarat dia mesti serahkan cincin 4 keramat kepadanya. Apabila Akil enggan, Anjang Itam mengugut hendak membunuh Cikgu Shila. Sebelum Anjang Itam sempat berbuat demikian, Siti, anak bomoh Tok Misai memukulnya. Anjang Itam ditangkap polis kerana dialah yang sebenarnya telah membunuh Tok Misai. Akil minta bantuan Pak Sudin untuk menghalau saka-saka tersebut dan menyerahkan cincin 4 keramat itu kepada Pak Sudin yang membuangnya kedalam tasik. Di situ tamatnya riwayat Jendul, Big Foot, Mayang Kasturi dan Kimchi (saka-saka). Pak Sudin menasihati Akil supaya jangan tinggal solat dan banyak membaca quran kerana makhluk halus akan menjauhkan diri daripada dia. Melihat perubahan Akil yang tidak lagi mendampingi saka-saka, Cikgu Shila berbaik semula dengan Akil. Pada suatu hari Akil telah membawa ibunya kerumah Chikgu Shila untuk mengeratkan lagi pertalian keluarga dan mungkin berkesudahan dengan perkahwinan antara Akil dengan Cikgu Shila

programme.title: The Hollow One
programme.desc: Rachel dan Anna pulang ke rumah dua tahun selepas kematian ibu mereka, dan dapati bandar itu ditinggalkan dengan rumah mereka dalam keadaan kacau dan kotor. Apabila Rachel mula mengalami halusinasi mengenai ibu mereka yang sudah meninggal dan sesuatu artifak purba, petunjuk-petunjuk menakutkan mula terbongkar mengenai masa lalu keluarga mereka.

programme.title: Double Barrel
programme.desc: Mengenai pasangan muda yang miskin bekerja sebagai pembunuh upahan sehingga mereka diberi tugasan terbaru untuk menghapuskan abang isteri sendiri yang memaksa mereka lari dan bersembunyi daripada kumpulan itu untuk menyelamatkan diri dan bayi mereka.

programme.title: Yang Berhormat
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Kuping, anak gelandangan yang menjalani kehidupan di Kuala Lumpur dengan melakukan pelbagai pekerjaan. Dia bersahabat dengan seorang OKU bernama Lobak dan Mat Yee. Pada suatu hari, Kuping terserempak dengan seorang lelaki bernama YB Salleh Ali dan terpesona melihat beliau memberi ceramah politik. Kuping yang terinspirasi dengan YB Salleh Ali itu ingin membantu Lobak untuk memikat seorang gadis bernama Mastura.

programme.title: Estet
programme.desc: Mengisahkan para pekerja estet Cinta Manis yang bakal bertarung dengan kumpulan estet Red Cobra dalam satu perlawanan bola sepak yang sudah 20 tahun tidak diadakan. Farid dan Shashi, dua pekerja estet yang berkawan sejak kecil, menjadi harapan pekerja estet yang lain untuk menyelamatkan penindasan yang dilakukan oleh kerani estet, Pooniah. Seorang gadis cantik bernama Geetha tertarik hati dengan Farid dan Shashi. Sesi latihan dikendalikan oleh Subramaniam iaitu bapa Geetha yang dilantik sebagai jurulatih. Ayah kepada Shashi, Apaa, adalah pemain bola yang sangat mahir, tetapi telah berlaku insiden semasa perlawanan bola sepak estet itu dahulu yang mana kakinya patah diterjah oleh Junna, seorang samseng estet yang sengaja ingin menamatkan karier Apaa atas upahan Pooniah 20 tahun yang lalu. Berjayakah Farid dan Shashi serta kawan-kawannya membebaskan pekerja estet Cinta Manis daripada penindasan Pooniah?

programme.title: Imigran
programme.desc: Faridah, pekerja warga asing terlibat dalam kes jenayah apabila telah menjadi saksi kes pembunuhan. Bertemu Hisham ketika cuba melarikan diri, mereka berdua mula jatuh cinta selepas menghabiskan masa bersama di kampung Hisham. Konflik berlaku apabila penjenayah tersilap menculik orang yang menyebabkan Faridah dan Hisham perlu melakukan sesuatu untuk menyelamatkan Azura.

programme.title: Setinggan
programme.desc: Kawasan setinggan yang dibangunkan di tapak kubur tali barut Jepun menimbulkan kekacauan terhadap penduduk di situ. Hantu-hantu kubur tersebut merayau dan menganggu ketenteraman penduduk di situ.

programme.title: Darah Satria
programme.desc: Filem yang menceritakan tentang tugas anggota angkatan tentera dan pengorbanan yang mereka lakukan demi negara yang tercinta, lakonan Aman Shah sebagai Leftenan Muda Rejimen Askar Melayu Di Raja.

programme.title: Siapa Tak Sayang Bini 2
programme.desc: Merupakan lanjutan daripada kisah dua keluarga yang ingin mengawal pasangan masing-masing. Kisah kali ini bermula apabila Saiful ternampak Karim yang sudah tidak takut isteri berjalan dengan seorang wanita muda bernama Sephia. Karim sering mendengar luahan Sephia yang sedang bergaduh dengan teman lelakinya. Saiful yang suka menyibuk itu memberitahu perkara tersebut kepada Kasmah, isteri Karim. Pelbagai kekalutan berlaku setelah Kasmah mengesyaki suaminya berlaku curang dan meminta bantuan Kamisah untuk menyiasat perkara ini. Dalam masa yang sama, Karim dengan bantuan Kassim mencari jalan untuk menjernihkan keadaan.

Hanya kerana ingin membuat jalan raya, bukit dan pokok ditebang manakala sungai dicemari sisa bahan toksik - menyebabkan ikan mati dan beracun. Sebuah penemuan merungkai segalanya.

programme.title: Ekspresi
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang kanak-kanak bernama Awi yang kurang mendapat kasih sayang daripada ibu bapanya yang sibuk bekerja. Awi sering bergaul dengan budak-budak nakal di sekitar rumahnya. Keadaan menjadi semakin keruh setelah Awi mengetahui bahawa dia merupakan anak angkat dan bakal mendapat adik baru. Hal ini telah membuatkan Awi semakin memberontak sehingga dia cuba untuk membunuh ahli keluarganya.

programme.desc: Mengisahkan Hisyam yang menjaga bapanya yang mengalami masalah sering lupa. Pada suatu hari, Hisyam berang kerana bapanya telah membuat sesuatu yang menyebabkan huru hara di pejabatnya. Bapanya sedih dengan kejadian itu dan berjanji tidak akan mengulanginya. programme.title: Blessing of Formosa (T) Ep224
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: My Kickass Wife
programme.desc: Jade is a beautiful royal guard who is set up for marriage by the Queen in order to avoid the King setting eyes on her. Jade falls for Sean and helps him win the contest for her. After the wedding, Sean discovers her bad temper and visits a brothel in his despair. He meets and is attracted to a girl there, not knowing she has a secret agenda...

programme.title: In the Mood for Love
programme.desc: This movie is Wong Kar Wais most acclaimed feature, navigating the subtle love relationship between Chow Mo Wan and Su Li Zhen after both discover their spouses having an affair with each other.

programme.title: Mad Fate
programme.desc: A Master fortune teller predicts that Tung, a born psychopath, will be imprisoned for murder and tries to change his fate. A veteran detective believes Tung is a psychopathic serial killer after witnessing him kill a cat, and pursues him relentlessly. Can the Master change Tungs mad fate?

programme.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
programme.desc: Donnie Yen plays a Hong Kong police officer who is highly skilled in martial arts but balloons to more than 200 pounds after his fianc left him. His boss can only assign simple tasks to him like escorting a criminal to Japan, but can he complete it?

programme.title: Lion Rock
programme.desc: Based on the true story of David Ki, one of Asias top rock climbers who lost everything when a motorcycle accident crippled him. Rather than succumbing to his fate, David found a way of scaling the dizzying peaks again by becoming a wheelchair-bound athlete and soon reached the peak of Lion Rock!

programme.title: The Brotherhood of Rebel
programme.desc: Chai, a triad member, helps his childhood friend Meow flee Hong Kong after discovering that Meow attempted to kill his triad boss. 17 years later, Chai becomes a key member of the triad. When he runs into Meow one day, he knows that his gang will kill Meow if they find him. Caught between triad and brotherhood, what will Chai choose?

programme.title: Young Ip Man: Crisis Time
programme.desc: Set in 1917, young Ip Man pursues his studies in Hong Kong. The school is held hostage on the day of an English speech competition, and as Ip Man decides to step up and fight the crisis, it is revealed that his master and his childhood friend are behind all this. Can he take them down and uphold justice?

programme.title: L Storm
programme.desc: ICAC officer Luk and Chief Inspector Lau both hit a dead end when investigating their respective bribery and money laundering cases. When Luk is accused of bribery after being framed by the money launderers, he risks everything he has to find crucial evidence against them to clear his name.

programme.title: Keep Rolling
programme.desc: Directorial debut of Man Lim Chung, who spent 3 years filming this documentary about the life and filmmaking philosophy of Ann Hui, one of Hong Kongs greatest filmmakers. It traces Huis life story and her 40-year careers ups and downs using film footages, candid conversations with Hui, and interviews with her collaborators, family and friends.

programme.title: Hand Rolled Cigarette
programme.desc: A retired British-Chinese soldier becomes a target in a triad manhunt when he takes in a young South Asian man who carries a bag of stolen drugs. Forced to live together, the two men transcend conflicts and cultural differences to form a beautiful friendship in this poignant tale of loyalty and brotherhood.

programme.title: Midnight Diner
programme.desc: A small restaurant in Shanghai is open only from midnight to early morning. The chef has no menu but will create something unique for each customer. Through the years, people come to the Midnight Diner to share their stories, taste the chefs delicious food and leave feeling comforted and fulfilled.

programme.title: Born to Fly
programme.desc: Lei Yu has officially become the new generation of Chinese test pilots after rounds of strict selection. Captain Zhang Ting leads Lei Yu and other pilots to test the latest fighter jets. Lei Yu keeps pushing the limits in each test flight in the hope of coming up with the perfect plane to ensure the safety of the fighter pilots.

programme.title: Love For All Seasons
programme.desc: May, acting leader of the Er Mei sect, cures the incurable illness of Tiger, a rich playboy. Under the threat of her senior, May seeks help from Tiger to experience heartbreak and master the "Heartbroken Sword" style, so as to defeat her senior and preserve Er Mei sect. Will this strange and long-winding relationship reach a happy ending?

programme.title: The Monkey King
programme.desc: After Goddess Nuwa sacrifices herself to save the mortal world, Monkey King comes into being from one of her crystals. Powerful and uncontrollable, Monkey King challenges the Jade Emperor and causes an uproar in heaven, unwittingly creating an opportunity for the wicked Buffalo Demon King to wage war in heaven.

programme.title: Push and Shove
programme.desc: A puppy gets gravely injured while defending them from the neighbor's large and aggressive Tibetan Mastiff. The arrogant owner of the Tibetan Mastiff, however, refuses to take responsibility, and the police aren't of much help since no people were hurt. When push comes to shove, the puppys owner vows to fight for justice for his dog.

programme.title: The White Storm
programme.desc: Three Narcotics Bureau officers who are good friends get involved in a case with the drug lord. When the operation fails, they must make a devastating decision - two can live, but one must die. Five years later, the two vow to take revenge but end up competing against each other for their own lives. Will brotherhood be sacrificed again?

programme.title: One Second
programme.desc: Directed by renowned director Zhang Yimou, the film is set during the Cultural Revolution, where a common man escapes a labour camp to find a newsreel that captures his daughter for one second in a movie. On the way, he encounters an orphan who also seeks the movie reel. Can the man finally pass the reel to a projectionist and screen the movie?

programme.title: The Fatal Raid
programme.desc: Twenty years after a deadly bloodbath between the Hong Kong Police and Macau gangsters, Madam Fong, the surviving team member, leads a new squad of four policewomen across borders to pursue young anarchists terrorizing Macau in a mission to protect the Hong Kong Polices Deputy Chief Commissioner.

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. While things seem to be falling apart, this dinner may well be an opportunity to mend relations.

programme.title: Inner Senses
programme.desc: Haunted by recurring visions stemming from past traumas, Yan reaches out to psychiatrist Dr Jim to restore her sanity and overcome her troubled past. Yet, as Yan gradually heals, Jim finds himself haunted by the same disturbing images, as his suppressed memories resurface.

programme.title: Mission Milano
programme.desc: A wealthy entrepreneur goes undercover with an Interpol agent to protect a new invention, the Seed of God, from falling into an international crime conglomerate.

programme.title: Wusong VS Ximenqing
programme.desc: Wu Song finds out about his sister-in-laws affair with a rich man, Ximen Qing. Qing sets Song up and have him exiled for a year, during which his hapless brother is murdered and cremated. When Song finally returns home, he takes the case to court but the judge brushes it aside and closes it abruptly. Can Song finally avenge his brothers death?

programme.title: Infernal Affairs II
programme.desc: In this prequel, the secrets of Infernal Affairs are revealed - the resentment between police superintendent Wong and crime boss Sam, as well as the beginning of the parallel fates of the two moles, Yan and Ming. The keys lie in the hands of Sam's wife, a ruthless kingpin and a righteous cop.

programme.title: Fallen Angels
programme.desc: The funkier cousin to Chungking Express, director Wong Kar Wai looks at five fallen angels who suffer love and loss amidst the crime and chaos of Hong Kongs neon nights in this movie. Karen Mok won Best Supporting Actress in the 15th Hong Kong Film Awards for her remarkable role as a broken-hearted party girl.

programme.title: Everything Under Control
programme.desc: During a diamond heist, one of the security escorts, Jelly, steals the diamonds and flees. Fellow security escorts, Yau Shing and Penguin, are forced to help the robber track down the diamonds. They stumble onto a remote village along the way, encountering strange villagers and mysterious incidents. Can they finally locate Jelly and the diamonds?

programme.title: Soul Mate
programme.desc: July and An Sheng have been best friends since they were thirteen. They always believed their friendship would last forever, until they meet Su Jia Ming at the age of eighteen. The trio find themselves in a love triangle, which puts the girls friendship to the test and alters their destinies.

programme.title: The Way We Keep Dancing
programme.desc: This sequel of The Way We Dance features the plight of Hong Kongs grassroots performing artists as they fight against the governments plan to gentrify an industrial district where they settled in.

programme.title: The Wandering Earth II
programme.desc: In this prequel, humans build enormous engines on the Earths surface to find a new home when the sun is burning out. In the dangerous universe, a group of young people has to step forward once again to fight in the critical battle to save the Earth.

programme.title: The Monkey King 2
programme.desc: Monkey King is tasked with escorting Monk Tang on his journey to the West to retrieve the scriptures. During the trip, Monk Tang is being targeted by the seductive yet deadly White Bone Spirit, who feeds on the innocents to gain immortality. Monkey King will have to fight the White Bone Spirit in order to save Monk Tang!

programme.title: 77 Heartwarmings
programme.desc: After breaking up with Adam, Eva focuses on her career but Adam still wants to make up and tries to move her 77 times. Things become more complicated when a Thai movie idol courts Eva. It is at this time that Evas mother becomes very ill, and she considers marriage in order to fulfil her mothers wish. Will Adam succeed in warming Evas heart?

programme.title: The Invisible Guest
programme.desc: Young and beautiful entrepreneur Joanna is a prime suspect in a locked-room murder where her lover is found dead. She pays off a police officer to prove her innocence. During the investigation, they discover another murder case involving Joanna and her lover, and eventually reveals the truth.

programme.title: Band Four
programme.desc: An aspiring singer of an indie band called Band Four reunites with her estranged guitarist father following the death of her mother. Together with her half-sister and her nine-year-old son, the newly reunited family come together to support each other through their love and passion for music.

programme.title: The Mighty One
programme.desc: Lung seeks five volumes of a renowned Kung Fu manual to gain invincibility. When he believes a martial arts school master possesses the volumes, he kills him and his daughter but leaves behind a young brother and sister. Years later, Lung loses two volumes and starts another bloody hunt but each attempt is interrupted by two mysterious warriors...

programme.title: Forever And Ever
programme.desc: Ivy Ling Po plays a young scholar who is manipulated into marrying a nobleman's reluctant daughter. After marrying, he soon discovers the reason for her hesitation. She is stricken with a contagious disease. But, with the power of true love, their romance prevails.

programme.title: The Vengeful Beauty
programme.desc: The Flying Guillotine assassins are secretly working for the Emperor and its leader Jin is sent to kill Hon, who knows this secret. Hons pregnant wife Rong seeks to kill Jin but retreats to protect her unborn child. When she is hunted down herself, Rong hooks up with a former Flying Guillotine member and her martial arts senior to fight back...

programme.title: Martial Arts of Shaolin
programme.desc: Zhi Ming, who trains at the Northern Shaolin Temple, teams up with Si Ma Yan, who trains at the Southern Shaolin Temple, to avenge both their fathers death by assassinating a corrupt magistrate, leading to a series of fierce battles!

programme.title: The Merry Wife
programme.desc: A 17-year old schoolgirl marries her 35-year-old teacher. Comedy ensues when they attempt to keep their relationship a secret despite being in the same school. When they discover unwanted suitors going after their other halves, jealousy threatens to expose their marriage any minute!

programme.title: Come Drink with Me
programme.desc: The brother of the mystery swordswoman "Golden Swallow is kidnapped. She joins forces with a beggar Drunken Cat who is skilled in martial arts to free her brother from a Buddhist monastery run by a corrupt abbot. The film was selected as Hong Kongs entry for the Best Foreign Language Film at the 39th Academy Awards.

programme.title: Lover's Rock
programme.desc: Pan Lei, winner the China Literary Award for three consecutive years, wrote and directed this film about the lives and loves of a fishing village. It starred the glorious Cheng Pei-pei in her first film as a woman (she had debuted in a mans role), and her much-lauded performance won her the prestigious Golden Accolade Award from the International Association Of Independent Producers a first for any Asian woman.

programme.title: The Lady is the Boss
programme.desc: Wong Hsia Yuan is a traditional kung fu master whose academy is on the brink of closure. Chan Mei Ling arrives from U.S. to revitalize the academy but her way of recruiting students is going beyond questionably legal. Yuan is furious, but when the local triads enter the picture, Yuan and Ling join hands to take back the neighborhood.

programme.title: Tragic Commitment
programme.desc: When the husband of a doctor, Tung is fatally wounded in an accident, he reveals to her about his affair with Blackie, who is impregnated with his baby. Despite the devastation of the betrayal and the eventual death of her husband, Tung is pressured by her mother-in-law into putting up with Blackie and offer $1M for her baby...

programme.title: Disciples of the 36th Chamber
programme.desc: In the finale of this trilogy, Gordon Liu reprises his famous role, Monk San Te, as he tries to protect Fang Shih Yu, an arrogant youth who gets into trouble with the Qing officials, and nearly lands Shaolin Temple into trouble too.

programme.title: Raw Passions
programme.desc: Mrs Lin's husband and his friend both have affairs with a belly dancer Sasa, and are both blackmailed by her. Sasa is stabbed one day and her brother shows up asking for money. A mysterious man also claims he can offer evidence for cash to help Lins husband. Lin has to unveil the deceit, double-crosses and blackmailing before she is in danger too!

programme.title: The Savage Five
programme.desc: A group of bandits flees with a stolen safe to a village where they oppress the villagers and force the blacksmith Wei to unlock the safe. Wei refuses and flees to report to officials, while heroes of the town emerge to fight the bandits.

programme.title: New Tales of the Flying Fox
programme.desc: In a great rendition of The Silver Fox and Legend of the Fox comes this exciting adventure, where the only thing between the clan leaders and certain death is Hui Ying-hung.

programme.title: Hex Vs Witchcraft
programme.desc: A compulsive gambler with bad luck owes money to a violent gangster boss and trades his wife as down payment, causing her to leave him. As he decides to kill himself, a mysterious old man offers him a proposal to marry the ghost of his dead daughter in exchange for cash and an expensive apartment.

programme.title: The Imperial Swordsman
programme.desc: Fu is a government officer heading home after being charged with falsifying reports. En route, he encounters & recruits a skilled swordsman as a bodyguard. They then meet a fleeing bride and her maid who asked to join them for protection. When the group reach a ruined temple however, a gang of assassins appear and attack them

programme.title: Dawn will Come
programme.desc: Liang Cai drugged the beautiful Qiu Rong and raped her, but promised to marry her after getting his parents consent. Since then, there is no news of his proposal and Qiu Rong confronts Liang Cai when she finds herself pregnant. This is when she discovers that he has already married a rich noble girl and even plans to kill her

programme.title: Two Champions of Shaolin
programme.desc: Set in the Qing Dynasty, the Shaolin clan wants to overthrow Qing and restore the Ming Dynasty, while the Wudang clan is backed by the Qing government. The two renowned clans eventually set themselves up against each other, and a series of vicious fighting has just begun

programme.title: Spring Blossoms
programme.desc: Some of Shaw Brothers' biggest female stars of the 1970s share the screen in this tale of young love and interfering parents, starring Lily Li, Shu Pei Pei and Essie Lin Chia.

programme.title: The Magnificent Trio
programme.desc: A group of farmers who are being oppressed by the local magistrates kidnap one of the magistrates daughter in the hope of being heard by the authorities. A wandering swordsman offers his help and aiding him are two fighters who have both switched sides from being the oppressors to the oppressed. The trio fight back against the magistrates!

programme.title: Fast Fingers
programme.desc: After his release from prison, Uncle Bill returns to make a fortune with his past thieving partners. They continue to prey on the unsuspecting public, but are closely watched by the upright police chief, who happens to be the boyfriend of one of Uncle Bills nieces!

programme.title: Angel with the Iron Fists
programme.desc: Lo Wei directs and stars as the chief detective in this gripping thriller; playing alongside Lily Ho, who excels in the role of an undercover avenger that can fight as well as she flirts! Caught between the crime bosses known as Baldhead and Black Widow, she only has four choices: punch, kick, shoot or bombard with explosives!

programme.title: The Last Tempest
programme.desc: This sequel to The Empress Dowager continues the tale of Emperor Guangxu and Empress Dowager Cixi. Despite Guangxus enthronement, his ability to rule effectively is overshadowed by the ever-present power of Cixi. When his attempts to reform the Imperial system are thwarted by the Empress Dowager, Guangxu attempts to curb her power.

programme.title: The Hidden Power Of Dragon Sabre
programme.desc: Defeated villain Sung Ching Shu returns and starts a reign of terror, trapping a beautiful Mongolian Princess and mastering the "yin and yang combination" to become almost invincible. Only two swords held by two great swordsmen can stand in his way!

programme.title: Torrent Of Desire
programme.desc: Rich playboy David is a drunk until he falls in love with a fashion model Dan Feng and marries her. David's sister Mona is in love with his best friend Han Ming, who rejected her as he secretly loves Dan Feng as well. Out of jealousy and hatred, Mona lies to David about a fake affair between Han Ming and Dan Feng...

programme.title: Lion VS Lion
programme.desc: The traditional lion dance has never looked so good as in Lion VS Lion which captures the most impressive sequences of lion dancing on film. Besides being loaded with enjoyable martial arts chicanery, film historians can revel because it's also the first film that clearly demonstrates the intricacies and differences between the traditional Northern and Southern lion dancing techniques. The Five Venom alumnus and Chang Cheh discovery, Lo Meng, teams up with Liu Chia-liang protege Wang Yu, as they inadvertently turn from vagabond kung-fu school operators into anti-Ching, patriotic fighters.

programme.title: The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This side-splitting comedy sees naive Ah Niu headed to Hong Kong, where he is repeatedly exploited and taken advantage of, and eventually finds himself arrested and imprisoned! Can he survive difficult times and finally overcome adversity?

programme.title: Opium And The Kung-Fu Master
programme.desc: Tie Qiao San, head of the Ten Guangdong Tigers, is an honourable master with many disciples. As opium becomes popular among the nobles, Tie starts taking it and gradually harms his body. When an opium houses owner defeats Tie in a fight and he is only saved from being killed by his disciple, Tie vows to quit opium and get back on his feet.

programme.title: Return of the Phoenix
programme.desc: An imperial minister Cheng betroths his pretty younger daughter, Ye, to his friend's son, Mu. His wife however, refuses to let Ye marry before her elder daughter Yan, who is ugly and undesirable. Yan is asked to pretend as Ye to meet Mu but scares him away. A rich guy who likes Ye meanwhile pretends as Mu to attend the wedding...

programme.title: King Cat
programme.desc: The son of the imperial teacher is beheaded by Justice Bao for corruption. Infuriated, the teacher hires assassins to kill Bao, who is saved by Zhan Zhao. Meanwhile, a royal treasure is stolen while a murder takes place. Bao is ordered to solve the case in ten days and Zhan quickly sets off to investigate. Will they solve the case in time?

programme.title: Scandal
programme.desc: The roguish scamp Zhen and his best friend Chia collects proof of corruption from the officials in this comedy-drama. After a string of blackmailing, they end up in positions of power, but what is to happen next?

programme.title: The Twin Swords
programme.desc: Gui Wu and his wife Gan Lian Zhu are the famous Twin Swords in the martial arts world. One day, they stumble upon a kidnapping plot at the Red Lotus Temple and Lian Zhu is held captive. Wu successfully escapes to find the Gan family for help, not knowing that he is sending them into an ambush by the kidnappers. Can he finally save Lian Zhu?

programme.title: When the Clouds Roll By
programme.desc: Su is a schizophrenic who refuses to believe that her pilot lover is killed in a plane crash and makes up stories to deal with things. She runs into an old classmate Lai, who is also a doctor one day, and he finds ways to treat her illness. Su slowly recovers and accepts the reality, as well as her newfound love.

programme.title: Ode to Gallantry
programme.desc: In this surprisingly light-hearted "Venoms" martial arts adventure, a lone wanderer is repeatedly mistaken for someone else and drawn into a number of violent battles.

programme.title: Call of the Sea
programme.desc: A young fisherman, Chin Hu is in love with his childhood friend Hsiao Yu. However, the only son of a town bully lusts after Hsiao Yus beauty and tries all possible ways to approach her. Chin Hu protects another woman from the bully one day, leading Hsiao Yu to misunderstand him and suspect that they are having an affair...

programme.title: Legendary Weapons of China
programme.desc: Lei Kung, the leader of the Boxer Clan in Yunnan, dissolves the clan to save his disciples before going into self-exile. The Clan sends various assassins to kill him but failed. They then assigned Kungs brother Yong to find and kill Kung, leading to a battle between the two brothers.

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: Zhang and Jins daughter, Peony, are betrothed at birth but Jin objects to the engagement now. Zhang meets a carp spirit that looks exactly like Peony and they fall in love. When Justice Bao is asked by Jin to distinguish Peony from her replica, he decides to quit the case when he witness the true love between Zhang and the carp spirit.

programme.title: Dew Drops Diaries Ep25
programme.desc: Flying High / Nest Sweet Nest - Marcus makes a Dew Drop-sized hot-air balloon for Phoebe and the Dews have a blast helping their kids from above, including secretly guiding Lola back to her family, before she accidentally follows Hip-Hop the frog out of the park. / Phoebe makes a pair of glasses for Bob the bird, but when seeing things clearly for the first time gets him lost, the Dews help Bob find his nest before his family arrives for a visit.

programme.title: Dragons: Rescue Riders Ep10
programme.desc: Slobber Power - Cutter gets a chance to be a "mom" when a newly hatched dragon bonds with him, and they'll both be needed to get the others out of a tangled mess.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep15
programme.desc: Gimme, Gimme, Gimme: The Game - King Julien becomes so enthralled with the idea of money that he introduces it to the kingdom.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep16
programme.desc: Body Double - In preparation for peace talks with the crocodiles, King Julien hires a body double to go in his place.

programme.title: Spirit Riding Free Ep15
programme.desc: Lucky And The New Governor - The girls plans to attend the Governors Ball are waylaid when they save a pregnant horse.

programme.title: Spirit Riding Free Ep16
programme.desc: Lucky And The Risky Rescue - When a Tuckapaw boy is unfairly arrested, Lucky and her friends plan to break him out of jail.

programme.title: Not Quite Narwhal Ep4
programme.desc: Crabby / Spe-shell - When Pixies pet crab goes into a cave, Kelp uses his knowledge of crabs under the sea to coax him out using dance and rhythm. / Scallops special shell is broken, but Kelp transforms the broken bits into something even more special.

programme.title: Dew Drops Diaries Ep22
programme.desc: Tooth on the Loose / That Thing You Dew - When Phoebe convinces the Tooth Fairy to visit before Marcus has actually lost his tooth, the Dew Drops do everything in their power to make sure the tooth is out before she arrives! / The Dews decide to hold a concert in the park for their animal friends, but cant find the time to practice.

programme.title: Dawn Of The Croods Ep19
programme.desc: There Will Be Eggs / I Think We're Alone Meow - Eep & Thunk want to be in on the new fad of Slateboarding, but must find something to trade with (eggs). Bud and Crud try to corner the egg market/Gran takes in a group of crabby tabbies, and uses their combined crabbiness to get whatever she wants. Grug and Ugga try to get into Snoot's food-sharing party.

programme.title: Dawn Of The Croods Ep20
programme.desc: Freepy Friday - Grug and Eep get into an argument and end up switching places to prove how hard it is to the other to be them. We follow Eep as the parent and Grug as the teenager at school and at home

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep22
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Bombastic Blathering of Brainy Blabulous - When Krupp transfers to another school, George and Harold follow, only to find a bizarro version of Jerome Horwitz Elementary, where the teachers are nice and the kids are well-behaved. But no one's having any fun! George and Harold want to right this wrong with pranks and comics. But Krupp enlists Mr. Neamer (bizarro Meaner), who then super-enlargers his brain and becomes Brainy Blabulous, in order to stop the subversion of authority.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep23
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Crazy Caustic Spray of the Contagious Cruelius Sneezer - In order to spice up their field trip to Romeinday (an ancient Rome reenactment park), George and Harold trick Melvin into turning the bus into a time machine so they can travel to actual ancient Rome and be gladiators. After offending Caesar with their comic, the emperor is accidentally turned into Cruelius Sneezer and pursues the school group with all his might.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep24
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Trashy Tale of the Tumultuous Tubbadump - In honor of Dump Day in Piqua- celebrating the creation of the dump - George and Harold try to earn extra credit by creating a trash-alanche. But Melvin creates an invention to suck all the trash into another dimension. The plan backfires when Tubbadump, a trash-covered monster, emerges from that dimension for revenge on the trashmakers.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep51
programme.desc: The Business Boss: Back in Baby - After the events of the Boss Baby 2 film, adult businessman Theodore Templeton is framed for embezzling from his company and forced to revert back to his old Boss Baby self and crash with his brother Tim. But to pull this off, he'll need to win over Tim's family into letting him stay, and convince Baby Corp to give him back his old job... which is currently held by his baby niece Tina.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep52
programme.desc: The Stroll - Tina and Boss adjust to co-boss responsibilities while on a mission to rescue the baby with the best hair in the world from a lice outbreak. With opposing leadership views, the two split the existing field team's focus and discover a new archenemy in Lumpy the Park Duck.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep53
programme.desc: Potty Mouth - After a baby says a swear word on live television (censored by child-friendly online filter Sheriff Potty Pardner), Boss becomes obsessed with proving that the baby was taught this filth by their new arch-nemesis, Lumpy the Park Duck. Meanwhile, Tina's search to find what that swear word means creates unintentional havoc for both Tabitha's research paper and for Baby Corp's online systems when Sheriff Potty Pardner gives them an "internet time out"

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Paws Of Destiny Ep1
programme.desc: Enter the Dragon Master - After absorbing the mystical Hero Chi of the Four Constellations, four panda kids enlist the Dragon Master to teach them Kung Fu

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Paws Of Destiny Ep2
programme.desc: Blue Dragon Plays with Fire - When the kids grow over-confident after beginning their training, they decide to intercept a distress call and sneak off without permission, only to land themselves in hot water

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Paws Of Destiny Ep3
programme.desc: Blade of the Red Phoenix - Po and the kids are recruited to perform in Mei Mei's theatrical show, but things take a turn when Jindiao ruins the play in order to find a mystical scroll

programme.desc: The Bunker List / The Interns - Branch bets Guy and Smidge that he can complete his Bunker List in one day/Satin and Chenille get the chance to intern for their idol Nova Swift

programme.desc: Three Trolls-keteers / The Helper - When a neighbor asks Guy for help to fight a monster, Guy mistakes it as an invite to act in his play/Smidge sets out to help Troll Village but creates disastrous results

programme.desc: Medieval Fest/ John Sutter - Sherman lets Mr. Hobson ride Captain Cools to beat Joan of Arc in a live joust competition; John Sutter creates a pig rush to discover the gold rush.

programme.title: Voltron: Legendary Defender Ep36
programme.desc: Black Site - Zarkon awakens from his coma and orders that Lotor is to be relieved of his duties, but Lotor is nowhere to be found

programme.title: The Adventures Of Puss In Boots Ep62
programme.desc: Dances With Dingoes - A laid-back, festival-loving dingo emerges from the portal and teaches the orphans to boogie, but Puss soon learns the dance instructor has secret intentions

programme.title: Turbo F.A.S.T. Ep36
programme.desc: Ransom Of White Shadow/Kicked Off - White Shadow is mistaken for a celebrity snail and kidnapped; Tito gets a foosball table which quickly becomes a soccer battle ground.

programme.title: Fifi and the Flowertots Ep71
programme.desc: Slugsy's Song - Slugsy has found something really special. Only Primrose can be persuaded to go and see it with him. Even she is surprised by what she sees!

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep19
programme.desc: The Case Of Bling's Hidden Present - It's Bling's birthday and she is so excited that she keeps opening all her presents before her party. Noddy needs to make sure she doesn't open the storybook present from him and Big Ears early but he's got to find it first! Big Ears has hidden it and can't remember where he's put it! Noddy launches his investigation to find the missing present before Bling does. Using his investigating skills Noddy follows the clues all over Toyland to find the present before the impatient little Naughticorn. At her birthday party Bling is thrilled to open the present from Noddy and Big Ears. She does have a present to open at her party after all! Well done Noddy!

programme.title: Fifi and the Flowertots Ep72
programme.desc: Stingo's Bridge - Webby has told Pip the story of the 3 Billy Goats Gruff. Soon a troll takes up residence under the bridge in the garden and demands food payment every time the tots cross. Can Fifi get to the bottom of the mystery?

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep20
programme.desc: The Case Of The Big Wall Of Bricks - Fuse has a new electronic ball. Noddy suggests that they invite everyone to play with it later. Fuse agrees but when Noddy returns with the other toys there is a big brick wall in front of the workshop. No one can get in and there's no sign of Fuse! Noddy uses all his investigating skills to follow the clues. He discovers that Fuse built the brick wall to stop his friends coming into the workshop because he was worried his new electronic ball might get broken. Noddy helps him feel comfortable with sharing his toy ball after all the other toys promise to be super careful with it. Now everyone can play together! Yay for Noddy!

programme.title: Roary The Racing Car Ep19
programme.desc: Heavy Loader - Roary takes Loada on a jaunt to the beach only to discover that sand and lorries don't mix too well!

programme.title: Roary The Racing Car Ep20
programme.desc: Testing Time For Maxi - PC Pete and Nick are up at Silver hatch giving the cars their road tests. Is Maxi really going to be as good as he says he is or will he be unpleasantly surprised?

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep19
programme.desc: Why Hare Hops - You see there was a time when Hare didn't hop. He was one of the speediest animals in Tinga Tinga but none of the other animals wanted to race with him because Hare always won and it was becoming boring.
